task.summary:
Node classes will now generate reports that are displayed in the report widget upon clicking on them in the node list widget. The class reports include a list of all inputs and outputs and the doc string if available.
This closes #6

task.summary: Re-arranged some code in the Loop nodes. Closes #2.
Added _return methods to nodes. TODO: Add calling node reference to return messages.
Fixed issue with non-loop control inputs. Graph editor can now be configured to close and return a node's return value.
Fixed KeyError when passing node reports to the painter module.
Removed saved graphs that are no longer compatible. Moved example graphs to 'example' directory. Added Simple line plot Node.
Fixed bug that caused crashes when deleting nodes.
Fixed issue with default values within loops.
